text: Gürbüz Lü (born 1943) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco- Roman 97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Samsun
